Description: Part of a limestone relief; Hieroglyphic text including the cartouches of Ptolemy I; frieze of stars above.
Curator's comments: Published: PM IV, p.68 S. Dhennin, Mefkat et la déese Hathor. Topographie et religion dans le IIIe province de Basse Egypte, MIFAO 146, Cairo 2022, p. 107 bloc no. 9.
Associated names: Named in inscription: Ptolemy I Soter I
